[size=5][b][color=#f38ba8]CrimsonForge Character Unlock[/color][/b][/size]
[size=3]Play as Damiane, Oongka, or Yahn in ALL chapters — no more waiting until the game decides you can.[/size]

[line]

[size=4][b]Description[/b][/size]

Crimson Desert locks your playable characters behind story progression. Damiane unlocks in Chapter 3, gets locked again from Chapters 5-8 with [i]"Comrade is on an important mission"[/i], and only returns at the end of Chapter 8. Oongka gets locked in Chapter 10+ and requires completing a specific faction quest.

This mod removes ALL character switching restrictions:

[list]
[*][b]No more "This is Kliff's story" popup[/b] — enter any chapter as any character without the forced Switch/Return dialog
[*][b]No more "Comrade is on an important mission"[/b] — all characters are always available on the switch screen
[*][b]Damiane playable in Chapters 5-8[/b] — no longer locked during the mid-game
[*][b]Oongka playable in Chapter 10+[/b] — no longer locked in endgame
[*][b]No more movement freeze[/b] — spawning locked characters no longer disables controls
[*][b]Free roam as any character[/b] — movement, combat, merchants, crafting all work
[*][b]Condition locks removed[/b] — 29 CheckCharacterKey conditions stripped from game data
[/list]

[size=3][color=#a6adc8]Built with enterprise-level reverse engineering. RTTI-verified vtable patches + data-level .pabgb modifications. Self-disabling on game updates — no crash risk.[/color][/size]

[line]

[size=4][b]What's Included[/b][/size]

This mod has [b]two components[/b]:

[size=3][b][color=#a6e3a1]1. Data Patches (Permanent)[/color][/b][/size]
Applied via CrimsonForge to game archives. Survive restarts. No runtime tool needed.

[list]
[*][b]Popup UI Patch[/b] — [font=Courier New]changecharacternoticepanel.html[/font]: timeScale=1 (no game pause), instant buttons, hidden visually
[*][b]Stage Forbidden Functions[/b] — [font=Courier New]stageinfo.pabgb[/font]: 14 entries renamed Forbidden→Permitted (prevents movement freeze)
[*][b]Condition Checks[/b] — [font=Courier New]conditioninfo.pabgb[/font]: 29 CheckCharacterKey(Kliff) conditions stripped
[*][b]Gimmick Conditions[/b] — [font=Courier New]gimmickgroupinfo.pabgb[/font]: 185 CheckCharacterKey(Kliff) entries for NPC interactions
[/list]

[size=3][b][color=#a6e3a1]2. Runtime Patch (Per-Launch via x64dbg)[/color][/b][/size]
The forbidden character list is generated by game code at runtime. Until a DLL loader is available, apply via x64dbg:

[list=1]
[*]Launch game to [b]main menu[/b] (don't load save)
[*]Attach x64dbg (with ScyllaHide, Denuvo profile)
[*]In command bar: [font=Courier New]disasm [CrimsonDesert.exe+4843218][/font]
[*]Press Space → type [font=Courier New]xor rax, rax[/font] → OK
[*]Type [font=Courier New]ret[/font] → OK → Cancel
[*]Press F9 → load your save
[*]All characters available — "Comrade is on an important mission" is gone
[/list]

[size=3][b][color=#a6e3a1]3. ASI Plugin (When Using CDUMM/ASI Loader)[/color][/b][/size]
If you have CDUMM or an ASI Loader installed, use the included [font=Courier New]CrimsonForgeCharUnlock.asi[/font] instead of x64dbg. It applies both patches automatically on game start.

[line]

[size=4][b]Installation — Data Patches[/b][/size]

Apply these once. They persist until Steam verifies files.

[size=3][b][color=#89b4fa]Using CrimsonForge (Recommended)[/color][/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Open CrimsonForge → Explorer tab
[*]Quick Mods menu → [b]Remove Condition Locks (CheckCharacterKey)[/b]
[*]Review preview → click [b]Apply + Patch to Game[/b]
[*]This patches both conditioninfo.pabgb (29 entries) and gimmickgroupinfo.pabgb (185 entries)
[*]stageinfo.pabgb and popup HTML are patched automatically
[/list]

[size=3][b][color=#89b4fa]Using CDUMM + ASI[/color][/b][/size]

[list=1]
[*]Install [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/crimsondesert/mods/84]CDUMM[/url]
[*]Open CDUMM → ASI Plugins tab → Install Plugin → select [b]CrimsonForgeCharUnlock.asi[/b]
[*]CDUMM auto-installs the ASI Loader
[*]Launch game — runtime patches applied automatically
[/list]

[size=3][b][color=#89b4fa]Uninstall[/color][/b][/size]

[list]
[*]Steam → Properties → Installed Files → Verify Integrity (restores all data patches)
[*]Delete ASI from CDUMM or bin64/scripts/
[/list]

[line]

[size=4][b]The 7 Restriction Layers[/b][/size]

[code]
Layer | System                              | Fix            | Status
------|-------------------------------------|----------------|--------
  1   | Forbidden character list (runtime)   | x64dbg/ASI     | BYPASSED
  2   | "Kliff's story" popup (runtime)      | HTML data patch | BYPASSED
  3   | Stage forbidden functions (data)     | stageinfo patch | PATCHED
  4   | Condition checks (data)             | conditioninfo   | PATCHED
  5   | Gimmick conditions (data)           | gimmickgroup    | PATCHED
  6   | Character change requirements (data) | characterchange | NOT NEEDED
  7   | Server switch rejection (runtime)    | Not applicable  | N/A (offline)
[/code]

